ain\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"my nose\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said 'stop'.\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's better to avoid [more harm] than to keep going.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"[more harm\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My nose started dripping from the first hit.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My nose\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"the first hit\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You need maturity even in this, and it's fine like this.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"maturity\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to go for my last kilometre for my father but I could not make it.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last kilometre\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I said to myself, for the experience I have and the maturity as a woman that I have got, I told myself, to my country and my dad, not to be mad at me, but I stopped [fighting].\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"the maturity\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said 'stop' for myself.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could be the match of my life, but in that moment I had to safeguard my life too.\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [